	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />What if there were programs to filter your screen into making it look like it's being played on NES?
<br />
<br />That would be cool.  Switchable options like low resolution filter, which basically pixellates the screen 2x2 pixels.
<br />
<br />Palette filter making things be displayed to only the 56(I think) colors NES can do.
<br />
<br />That would be so crazy, but cool.  Maybe a C64 render.
<br />
<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://img224.imageshack.us/img224/2194/c64vz7.png">http://img224.imageshack.us/img224/2194/c64vz7.png</a><!-- m -->
<br />
<br />I got bored and did this.  I mean I know it's not officially correct, like how 8x8 pixel tiles are only limitted to 4 colors, but it's better than nothing.

		

		</td>
